import React from "react"; import styled from "styled-components"; const TitleAndFilter: React.FC = () =>{ return ( 들어온 요청 파트너님에게 딱 맞는 요청서를 찾아보세요 가공방식 재료
) } export default TitleAndFilter const Container =styled.div` width: 80%; margin: 0 auto; margin-top: 2rem; ` const Title = styled.h1` color: ${props=> props.theme.color.gray}; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; ` const Subscription = styled.div` margin-top: 1rem; color: ${props=> props.theme.color.gray}; font-size: 16px; ` const Filter =styled.div` ` const ProcessingButton =styled.div` ` const MaterialButton = styled.div` ` const Processing =styled.form` ` const Matter = styled.form` `
